## util::def syntax

test critcl-util-def-1.0.6 {util-def, wrong\#args, not enough} -constraints tcl86plus -body {
    critcl::util::def
} -returnCodes error -result {wrong # args: should be "critcl::util::def configfile define ?value?"}

